'''科洛切普岛'''（{{lang-hr|Koločep}}，{{IPA-sh|kɔ̂lɔtʃɛp|pron}}），当地人称'''卡拉马塔岛'''（{{lang-it|Calamotta}}），是{{tsl|en|Elaphiti Islands|埃拉菲蒂群岛}}三大岛屿之一，邻近[[杜布羅夫尼克|杜布羅夫尼克]]，面积{{convert|2.44|km2|2|abbr=off}}<ref name="Duplancic-Cala-Ujevic">{{cite journal |url=https://hrcak.srce.hr/9636 |title=Coastline lengths and areas of islands in the Croatian part of the Adriatic Sea determined from the topographic maps at the scale of 1 : 25 000 |journal=Geoadria |location=Zadar |volume=9 |issue=1 |pages=5–32 |date=June 2004 |last1=Duplančić Leder |first1=Tea |last2=Ujević |first2=Tin |last3=Čala |first3=Mendi |doi=10.15291/geoadria.127 |format=PDF |accessdate=2019-12-26 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023024030/https://hrcak.srce.hr/9636 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是克罗地亚最南端的有人岛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rtl.hr/zivotistil/edukacija/3337879/znate-li-koji-je-najjuzniji-hrvatski-otok/|title=Znate li koji je najjužniji hrvatski otok|date=12 February 2019|work=rtl.hr|language=hr|accessdate=25 December 2019|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225201335/https://www.rtl.hr/zivotistil/edukacija/3337879/znate-li-koji-je-najjuzniji-hrvatski-otok/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年人口普查显示该岛有163人<ref name="2011 census">{{Croatian Census 2011|S|19|0981}}</ref>。

岛上最早的人类定居遗迹可追溯到[[古希腊|古希腊]]时期<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://hrcak.srce.hr/9735|title=Suvremena geografska problematika otoka Lopuda i Koločepa|trans-title=Recent Geographical Problematics of the Lopud and Koločep Islands|journal=Geoadria|volume=4|issue=1|year=1999|pages=91|last1=Glamuzina|first1=Martin|last2=Glamuzina|first2=Nikola|doi=10.15291/geoadria.152|language=hr|format=PDF|accessdate=25 December 2019|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003004518/https://hrcak.srce.hr/9735|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[拉古薩共和國|拉古薩共和國]]时期，该岛是重要的造船地。[[克里斯托弗·哥伦布|克里斯托弗·哥伦布]]率领的[[圣玛利亚号|圣玛利亚号]]下有两名水手便来自这座岛。岛上有古代欧洲征服者的考古遗迹，从古希腊及罗马时期，到[[拿破仑一世|拿破仑一世]]时期。岛上有七座前罗马式教堂，其历史可追溯至9世纪至11世纪克罗地亚列王时期。

